column216: Lecture content and assignments should be more transparent and relavent . Some times is difficult to understand assignment requirements.
sometimes I forget that I have access to my lecturers and that I can approach them with questions outside class. Back home, our lecturers are like “gods”. You approach with caution
I need some samples of assessments done before so that I can understand the level or standard of assessment expected.
I’m inclined to believe someone with zero background on computer science or programming would really struggle with keeping up with the program here.
